I said, ``There are two of us here in this room, just two men.'' And
I said, ``We _ it's a unique situation. Between us, we have the
power to start World War III. Or, between us, we have the power to
bring peace to the world, a lasting peace.'' And apparently, we've
been working in that direction.
   Q: Mr. President, if the Soviet Union makes good on it, and does
